---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 335
  - Title: Majjhima-nikâya
    Location: II 32
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Work, Action and Society=On ‘Karma’ and ‘Karma Yoga’
  - 700
---
I will teach you dhamma： if this is, that comes to be; from the
arising of this, that arises; if this is not, that does not come to
be; from the ceasing of this, that ceases.
